---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const calUrl = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_CAL_URL || "https://cal.com/southlike";
---

<Layout title="Obrigado — Southlike Software" noindex={true}>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pb-28 pt-24 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <div class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-500/10 ring-1 ring-brand-500/20">
        <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-balance text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
        Obrigado pelo Contato
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-neutral-300">Próximos passos:</p>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl space-y-3 text-sm text-neutral-300">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          Você receberá uma mensagem via WhatsApp em até 2 horas
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          Agendaremos uma conversa estratégica de 20 minutos
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          Se houver alinhamento, iniciamos a implementação
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400">
          Quer acelerar?
          <a href={calUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-brand-400 transition hover:text-brand-300">
            Agende direto pelo Cal.com
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-neutral-400 underline transition hover:text-white">Voltar ao site</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
